## Operator Breakdown

- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: savior|facilitator — The hero is no longer savior but facilitator. Identity reframed from conqueror to enabler.
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: lone_genius|shared_capacity — From individual genius to collective capacity. Others can now act; the return enables rather than imposes.
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: dominance|service — Mythic status detached from superiority and attached to service. The hero makes others able.
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: enlargement|lightening — Returns lighter, not larger. Growth through ego reduction rather than power accumulation.
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: hero_journey|capacity_distribution — The hero journey cycles into distributed capacity, feeding collective capability.
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: superiority|collective_uplift — Anti-domination myth: collective uplift over individual status.

## Z-State
